title: Studio Acapellas HipHop.EDM.Mainstream
description:
This is my first upload, I felt the need to share this because it's near impossible to find quality Acapellas for Remixs/Production. 



The Pack contains Acapellas from Pop/Mainstream to Hip Hop and EDM 

- Ariana Grande
- Zedd
- Fetty Wap 
- Lana Del Ray
- Kid Ink
- The Weekend
- Becky G 
- Ellie Goulding
- Big Sean
- Ed Sheeran
- And May More



In this torrent the keys of the acapella are in the file name by using the Camelot System. Info on the camelot system can be found here . So 5A = C Minor 6A = G Minor EXT



If you have a request for an Acapella leave it in the comments



Thanks AND PLEASE SEED
